    "media:imagetext": "Get Volvo quality\ntax and duty free!\nMany people qualify.\nIf you're a tourist, a diplomat or a business-\nman travelling or temporarily living abroad,\nyou can get a brand new Volvo at tax and\nduty free conditions. Just mail the coupon\nfor details.\nSAS\nRevised\nWorldwide\nTimetable\nNOV 1 1974-\nMARCH 31 1975\nAS\nDG8\nSAS\nTo: AB Volvo, Car Division, Tourist \u0026 Diplomat Sales,\nS-40508 Gothenburg, Sweden.\nYes, I'd like more information about tax and duty free condi-\ntions concerning 1974 Volvos. I want it equipped to comply with\nthe regulations\nof\n(country)\nName:\nAddress:\nPhone No:\nVOLVO\nTOURIST \u0026 DIPLOMAT SALES\nSAS SCANDINAVIAN AIRLINES\nSTOHM 982900",
